                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">on the two first Counts.</hi>
                  </rs> Aged 19.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18460921-1864-punishment-87" type="punishmentDescription">
