                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1864-18460921 t18460921-1864-punishment-87"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</hi> (Mr. Bodkin stated that the prisoner has been ten times in custody, ana several times convicted of felony.)</p>
